09:05.372 --> 09:07.673
The bubbles... very soothing.

09:09.009 --> 09:10.943
Mother. What are you doing here?

09:10.978 --> 09:12.778
You should be at home, resting.

09:12.813 --> 09:14.814
Please. How can I possibly rest?

09:14.848 --> 09:15.882
There's a murderer to catch.

09:15.916 --> 09:18.451
Listen, I-i have to warn you...
We found evidence

09:18.485 --> 09:20.653
that Robyn may have
returned to a life of crime.

09:20.687 --> 09:22.722
Nonsense. That girl has a good heart.

09:22.756 --> 09:24.857
I know she was trying
to turn her life around.

09:24.892 --> 09:27.293
So let's get to work.
What can I do to help?

09:27.327 --> 09:28.489
All right.

09:28.529 --> 09:31.564
We know that Robyn was
meeting with her new crew

09:31.598 --> 09:33.199
twice a week in Spanish Harlem.

09:33.233 --> 09:35.635
And I think these symbols on her phone

09:35.669 --> 09:37.970
have something to do with her next meeting.

09:38.005 --> 09:39.492
So, what's the problem?

09:39.795 --> 09:41.651
I don't speak emoji.

09:43.075 --> 09:45.292
I think that first symbol there...

09:45.371 --> 09:47.429
The buttony thing... is a clock, obviously.

09:47.508 --> 09:49.482
Uh-huh, and the hands are on 12,

09:49.516 --> 09:51.217
so Robyn's crew is meeting at noon.

09:51.251 --> 09:53.219
Not noon... midnight.

09:53.253 --> 09:55.721
So that gives us less than an hour

09:55.756 --> 09:57.323
to figure this out and get uptown.

09:57.357 --> 10:01.327
Okay, so we have a sheep,
an ear, a "d," a bull,

10:01.361 --> 10:04.397
a bag, a beach ball, and a fish on a pole.

10:04.431 --> 10:06.999
Emojis are symbolic for other things.

10:07.034 --> 10:09.936
Clearly,
but symbolic for what other things?

10:09.970 --> 10:11.504
Well, where would you go fishing?

10:11.538 --> 10:12.271
Water.

10:12.306 --> 10:13.606
By the river.

10:14.214 --> 10:15.608
What does that have to do with sheep?

10:15.642 --> 10:19.111
Well, emojis are often compound words,

10:19.146 --> 10:22.949
so "sheep" plus "ear"...

10:22.983 --> 10:24.884
Plus "d" could mean...

10:24.918 --> 10:26.352
Sheep eared. Shepherd.

10:26.386 --> 10:28.754
- Shepherd.
- Exactly.

10:28.789 --> 10:30.790
- And the bull?
- Stubborn?

10:30.824 --> 10:32.892
Wall street? That's not in Spanish Harlem.

10:32.926 --> 10:35.695
Bull is the astrological sign for Taurus.

10:35.729 --> 10:37.363
It is. Does that help us?

10:37.397 --> 10:38.464
We'll put a pin in that.

10:38.498 --> 10:39.799
Next are the bag and the ball.

10:39.833 --> 10:42.535
Oh. And not just any bag.

10:42.569 --> 10:44.470
That is a shopping bag.

10:44.504 --> 10:46.405
An item with which you
are intimately familiar.

10:46.440 --> 10:47.807
So, shopping ball?

10:47.841 --> 10:50.576
No... mall. Shopping mall.

10:50.611 --> 10:52.011
Wait a minute.

10:53.413 --> 10:54.814
Midnight by the river

10:54.848 --> 10:57.783
at the Shepherd Taurus shopping mall?

10:58.986 --> 11:00.753
Ohhhh!

11:00.787 --> 11:02.888
Well done. Let's go.

11:02.923 --> 11:04.624
Wait, wait. Shouldn't we call the cops?

11:04.658 --> 11:06.592
Yeah,
that's a kind of dangerous neighborhood.

11:06.627 --> 11:09.061
Ladies,
with all the gentrification going on,

11:09.096 --> 11:11.130
there's no such thing as
bad riverfront property.

11:12.299 --> 11:14.433
Okay. Maybe I was wrong.

11:16.303 --> 11:18.204
Watch your step.

11:19.206 --> 11:22.074
Maybe we should be texting Espo and Ryan.

11:22.109 --> 11:24.143
I already called them.
They're on their way.

11:24.177 --> 11:26.646
I don't know whether to be happy or hurt

11:26.680 --> 11:28.614
by your lack of faith in me.

11:29.850 --> 11:31.012
Okay, I'm gonna go with happy.

11:31.051 --> 11:33.386
- Was that a rat?
- That's too big to be a rat.

11:33.505 --> 11:35.919
- Great.
- Come on.

